## Design System

### Typography
- Font family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif
- Body: 16px / 1.5 line-height
- H1: 32px bold | H2: 24px bold | H3: 20px semibold | H4: 16px semibold
- Caption: 12px | Label: 14px medium

### Colour Palette
- Primary: #3B82F6 (blue-500)
- Primary dark: #1D4ED8 (blue-700)
- Success: #22C55E (green-500) — confirmations only
- Error: #EF4444 (red-500) — destructive actions and errors only
- Warning: #F59E0B (amber-500)
- Surface: #FFFFFF | Background: #F9FAFB | Border: #E5E7EB
- Text primary: #111827 | Text secondary: #6B7280 | Text muted: #9CA3AF

### Spacing Scale (rem)
0.25 | 0.5 | 0.75 | 1 | 1.5 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 6 | 8 | 12 | 16

### Border Radius
- Small: 4px (inputs, badges) | Medium: 8px (cards, buttons) | Large: 12px (modals) | Full: 9999px (pills)

### Shadow
- sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05) | md: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07) | lg: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)

### Component Rules
- All buttons: 44px min height, 8px horizontal padding, disabled state with 50% opacity
- All inputs: 40px height, 1px border, focus ring 2px primary
- All interactive elements: visible focus ring for keyboard navigation
- Loading states: skeleton UI (not spinner) for data fetches
- Toast notifications: bottom-right, 4s auto-dismiss
